SIMPLE: intermingle
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Intermingle
<hw>In`ter*min"gle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To mingle or
mix together; to intermix.</def> <rj><au>Hooker.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Intermingle</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Intermingle
<hw>In`ter*min"gle</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To be mixed or
incorporated.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Party and faction will <qex>intermingle</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Swift.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Intermise</ent>⟦br⟧
